A man died after a bakkie overturned on Groot Elandsvlei Road in Krugersdorp on Sunday.According to reports the accident happened around 21:30 and the man was the only occupant in the bakkie at the time of the accident.The man was freed from the wreckage by rescue officials and declared dead on scene by paramedics.Arrive Alive said: &#8220;Netcare911 paramedics worked alongside officials from the Krugersdorp Fire Department on scene.&#8221;-TNA Reporter